Corporate Social ResponsibilityReport 2016



At DHI, we don’t just provide solutions, we provide sustainable and environmentally-sound solutions to societies. We are committed to contributing to sustainable development with our technology. Read about the work we do in our 2016 CSR Report.






                        &nbsp&nbsp&nbsp
                    


Our software catalogue gives you an introduction to our comprehensive and versatile range of software products for water environments. Read about main news in MIKE 2017 as well as an almost endless number of application areas, features and modules.
Browse the Software Catalogue 2017 for the latest information.










DHI, UNEP-DHI and New Zealand Hydrological Society’s new initiative to bring Aqua Republica to New Zealand
We are embarking on a new campaign, together with our partners, to produce a local New Zealand version of Aqua Republica to promote water and environmental stewardship amongst New Zealand’s youth. 
                





