Ensuring sustainable aquaculture production in Chile
To ensure consistent and environmentally-sustainable aquaculture production in a market worth 4,000 million USD a year, the Institute for Fisheries and Aquaculture Research (IFOP) implemented DHI’s technology in their solution.







